{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f1a2dac818","title":"给毛岸英的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"46be15211e","index":0,"year":1947,"month":10,"day":8,"articleId":"f1a2dac818"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"e62e1d349d","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f1a2dac818","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":4,"text":"毛岸英，毛泽东的长子。"},{"id":"ead180da55","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f1a2dac818","index":2,"part_index":2,"offset":6,"text":"永寿，即毛岸青，一九二三年生，毛泽东的次子。"},{"id":"7060605631","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f1a2dac818","index":3,"part_index":2,"offset":121,"text":"李讷，一九四○年生，毛泽东之女。"}],"contents":[{"id":"466608f807","type":"title","text":"给毛岸英的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f1a2dac818"},{"id":"e62e1d349d","type":"appellation","text":"岸英：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f1a2dac818"},{"id":"ead180da55","type":"paragraph","text":"告诉你，永寿回来了，到了哈尔滨。要进中学学中文，我已同意。这个孩子很久不见，很想看见他。你现在怎么样？工作，还是学习？一个人无论学什么或作什么，只要有热情，有恒心，不要那种无着落的与人民利益不相符合的个人主义的虚荣心，总是会有进步的。你给李讷写信没有？她和我们的距离已很近，时常有信有她画的画寄的，身体好。我和江青都好。我比上次写信时更好些。这里气候已颇凉，要穿棉衣了。再谈。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f1a2dac818"},{"id":"7060605631","type":"paragraph","text":"问你好！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f1a2dac818"},{"id":"a4f09340f5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f1a2dac818"},{"id":"7cf06959b8","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四七年十月八日","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f1a2dac818"},{"id":"8072b437f9","type":"paragraph","text":"根据人民出版社一九八三年出版的","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f1a2dac818"},{"id":"ada7120fdd","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东书信选集》刊印。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f1a2dac818"}],"page":{"id":"208f6e4bfc","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f1a2dac818","start":320,"end":320}}}},"__N_SSG":true}